Sunway Sitges International (2019), Round 9
Sicilian, closed (B23)

1. e4 c5 2. Nc3 d6 3. Bb5+ Nd7 4. a4 Nf6 5. f4 a6 6. Bc4 e6 7. d3 Be7 8. Nf3 O-O 9. O-O b6 10. Qe1 Bb7 11. Bb3 Rc8 12. e5 Ne8 13. Bd2 g6 14. f5 gxf5 15. exd6 Nxd6 16. Ne2 Bxf3 17. Rxf3 Ne5 18. Rg3 Qf6 35. d4 Rc3 36. Rg5 b4 37. Ne5 b3 38. Rd1 b2 39. Nxg6 fxg6 40. Rxg6 Rc1 41. Rxf6 Rxd1+ 42. Kf2 Rxb1 43. Kg3 Rc1

The 6th Sunway Sitges International is a 10-round Swiss open taking place from 13-22 December 2019 in the Hotel Sunway Playa Golf & Spa in Sitges, Spain.

Players receive 90 minutes for 40 moves, followed by 30 minutes to the end of the game, plus a 30-second increment starting from move one. Official website: www.sunwaychessfestival.com
